snippet.title: Super Free Kick set 1 MAME Gameplay video Snapshot -Rom name sfkick-
snippet.description:
This video is a snapshot Super Free Kick (set 1) game sample video. Currently I have over 4000 videos gameplays completing almost full MAME romset.

You can download this sample video to add in the frontend for GameEx, HyperSpin, Mala, MameWAH, Maximus Arcade, XBMC and more. Super Free Kick (set 1) is a gameplay video demo rendered in high quality with a 480p resolution.

The original MAME rom name for this game is sfkick.
